hcc_text: Sedgwick Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At Sedgwick Avenue at West Mosholu Parkway South and Goulden Avenue, there was 1 severe injury in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
